 Problem Statement

Many people lack reliable, personalized tools for calculating their daily calorie requirements and optimal macronutrient distribution based on their own physical characteristics and lifestyle. Without these insights, it's easy to make poor dietary choices, follow ineffective workout routines, and risk undermining personal health goals.
